Crie um resolvedor:

public static String[] resolveMethodAndPath(
    String operationId,
    Map<String, String[]> swaggerEndpoints
) {
    if (swaggerEndpoints != null) {
        String[] swaggerEndpoint =
            swaggerEndpoints.get(operationId);

        if (
            swaggerEndpoint != null
                && swaggerEndpoint.length >= 2
        ) {
            return new String[]{
                swaggerEndpoint[0].toUpperCase(),
                swaggerEndpoint[1]
            };
        }
    }

    return inferMethodAndPath(operationId);
}

E onde atualmente existe:

String[] methodAndPath =
